sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant C as Client (Gerente)
    participant LC as LogsController
    participant LS as LogsService
    participant LR as LogsRepository
    participant DB as Database

    Note over C,DB: 1 · Consulta de trilha de auditoria — RF022 · RF024 · RN23 · RN24

    C->>+LC: GET /audit/logs?event_id={id}&shift_id={id}&page={n}
    Note over LC: requireAuth — JWT obrigatório
    LC->>+LS: getLogs(filters)
    LS->>+LR: findLogs({ event_id, shift_id, page })
    LR->>+DB: SELECT logs JOIN shifts WHERE filters<br/>ORDER BY timestamp DESC LIMIT 50 OFFSET n
    Note over DB: Campos retornados: id, shift_id, type,<br/>old_value, new_value, author_id, author_role,<br/>checkpoint_id, justification, created_at
    DB-->>-LR: log rows[]
    LR-->>-LS: logs[]
    LS-->>-LC: { logs[], total, page }
    LC-->>-C: 200 { logs: [ { id, type, old_value, new_value, author, timestamp, justification } ], total, page }

    Note over C,DB: 2 · Geração automática de log (via correção retroativa)

    Note over C: Gerente corrige checkpoint via PATCH /audit/checkpoints/:id
    C->>+LC: PATCH /audit/checkpoints/{id} { distance, justification }
    LC->>+LS: correctCheckpoint(...)
    LS->>+LR: correctCheckpoint + insertLog(shift_id, type, old_value, new_value, author_id, role)
    LR->>+DB: UPDATE checkpoints SET distance, old_distance, reviewed=true ...<br/>INSERT INTO logs (shift_id, type, checkpoint_id, old_value, new_value, ...)
    Note over DB: Log é imutável — nenhum DELETE ou UPDATE permitido na tabela logs
    DB-->>-LR: { checkpoint, log_id }
    LR-->>-LS: result
    LS-->>-LC: updated checkpoint
    LC-->>-C: 200 { id, shift_id, distance, old_distance, reviewed, reviewed_at }

    Note over C,DB: 3 · Sem logs para o filtro informado

    C->>+LC: GET /audit/logs?shift_id=999
    LC->>+LS: getLogs({ shift_id: 999 })
    LS->>+LR: findLogs(...)
    LR->>+DB: SELECT ... WHERE shift_id = 999
    DB-->>-LR: []
    LR-->>-LS: []
    LS-->>-LC: { logs: [], total: 0, page: 1 }
    LC-->>-C: 200 { logs: [], total: 0, page: 1 }
